      <h1>ELLIPAL is now on Desktop</h1>

      <p>Hi there,</p>

      <p>We are excited to share that the ELLIPAL Desktop App is officially=
 available for both Windows and macOS.</p>

      <p>Our team has been working to bring the full power of air gapped cr=
ypto security directly to your operating system. The desktop experience off=
ers meaningful advantages over the mobile version, including a larger portf=
olio dashboard for easier asset tracking, advanced on device scam detection=
 to help protect your holdings, and a built in AI assistant to guide you th=
rough portfolio decisions and market conditions.</p>

      <p>By running natively on your computer, whether you are on Windows o=
r macOS, the app delivers a faster, more comprehensive environment for mana=
ging your digital assets. You will also enjoy seamless firmware updates for=
 your hardware wallet directly through the desktop interface, ensuring your=
 device is always running the latest security patches.</p>

      <p>We have also enhanced the portfolio experience with tools designed=
 specifically for active crypto investors, including multi account manageme=
nt, real time price alerts, and a unified view of your balances across all =
your wallets in one place.</p>

      <div class=3D"button-container">
        <a href=3D"https://www.ellipalwallet.io/" class=3D"button">Download=
 ELLIPAL Desktop</a>
      </div>

      <p style=3D"font-size: 13px; color: #777777; text-align: center; marg=
in-bottom: 30px;">If the button above does not work, copy and paste this li=
nk into your browser:<br><a href=3D"https://www.ellipalwallet.io/" style=3D=
"color: #0E69F9; word-break: break-all;">https://www.ellipalwallet.io/</a><=
/p>

      <p>The installation takes just a minute, and your existing ELLIPAL ha=
rdware wallet connects seamlessly via secure QR codes.</p>

      <p>We look forward to hearing your feedback on the new experience.</p=
>

